= TTF_SizeText =

Get the dimensions of a rendered string of text 

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
int TTF_SizeText(TTF_Font *font, const char *text, int *w, int *h);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
|'''text'''
|text to render
|-
|'''w'''
|output width
|-
|'''h'''
|output height
|}

== Return Value ==

Returns 0 if successful, -1 on error

